(b) Compute $H + A$.

(c) Compute $2B - 3G$.

(d) Compute $2B + H$.

(e) Compute $B + H$.

(f) Compute $2D + 3F$.

(g) Compute $M$ if $2A + 2M + E = 3E - 2H + A$.

(h) Compute $N$ if $2D + 2N + F = 3N - D + 3C$.

